<div class="container">

<div class="row">
<!-- COLUMN #1 -->
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8" align="center">
      <h2 align="center">Karaoke <em>3.0</em></h2>
        <br><br>
        <%= image_tag "Karaoke.jpg", :height => '50%', :width => '85%', :class => 'img-circle img-responsive', :alt => 'Karaoke Singers' %>
        <!-- <p>Karaoke + Social Networking = Shareaoke</p> -->
    </div>
      <br>
      <br>
<!-- COLUMN #2 -->
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
      <h4>Sign Up</h4>
      <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <%= f.error_notification %>

        <div class="form-inputs">
          <%= f.input :email, required: true, autofocus: true %>
          <%= f.input :stagename, required: true, hint: "Choose wisely! Stage Name can't be changed." %>
          <%= f.input :password, required: true, hint: ("#{@minimum_password_length} characters minimum" if @minimum_password_length) %>
          <%= f.input :password_confirmation, required: true %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <%= f.button :submit, "Sign up" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
        <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
    </div>

  </div> <!-- end row #1 -->

<!-- Row #2 -->
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-1" align="left">
       <h4 align="left"><em>How Shareaoke Works:</em></h4>
        <div class="media" align="left">
          <div class="media-left">
            <a href="#">

              <%= image_tag "Pencil.png", :height => '35px', :width => '35px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="media-left">
            <h5 class="media-heading">Sign Up</h5>
            Takes less than 20 seconds &amp; there's nothing to download. All you need is a browser &amp; an email address. Customize your profile &amp; you're in business.
          </div>
        </div>
    <hr>
        <div class="media" align="left">
          <div class="media-left">
            <a href="#">
              <%= image_tag "Search.png", :height => '35px', :width => '35px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="media-left">
            <h5 class="media-heading">Check In</h5>
            Find your bar &amp; check into it. See who else has checked in &amp; where you are in the request queue.
          </div>
        </div>
    <hr>
        <div class="media" align="left">
          <div class="media-left">
            <a href="#">
              <%= image_tag "Music.png", :height => '35px', :width => '35px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="media-left">
            <h5 class="media-heading">Request your song</h5>
            Search the playlist to find the track you want to sing. Select it &amp; confirm the request. The DJ will get your request &amp; you'll be put in queue. That's it! Warm up your pipes &amp; wait for the DJ to call your stagename.
          </div>
        </div>
    <hr>
        <div class="media" align="left">
          <div class="media-left">
            <a href="#">
              <%= image_tag "Mic.png", :height => '35px', :width => '35px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="media-left">
            <h5 class="media-heading">Perform</h5>
            Shed the nerves &amp; do what you came to do!  When you're done performing the DJ will move you out of that queue &amp; others can rate the performance.
          </div>
        </div>
    <hr>
        <div class="media" align="left">
          <div class="media-left">
            <a href="#">
              <%= image_tag "Repeat.png", :height => '35px', :width => '35px', :class => 'img-square', :alt => 'Happy White People' %>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="media-left">
            <h5 class="media-heading">Repeat</h5>
            'Nuff said, Superstar! It's your world now. We're all just livin' in it. Perform again, &amp; again. Become the ruler of your favorite karaoke spot. Compete for leaderboard bragging rights.
          </div>
        </div>
    <hr>
